{"word":"Libnah","slug":"libnah","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Libnah</b> <a href=\"#/H3841\">H3841</a> <br/> 1. A station of the Israelites in the desert<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=33&verse=20'>Num 33:20</a><br/> 2. A city of Judah:<br/> - Captured by Joshua<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=10&verse=32'>Jos 10:32</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=10&verse=39'>Jos 10:39</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=12&verse=15'>Jos 12:15</a> <br/> - Allotted to the priests<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=21&verse=13'>Jos 21:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=6&verse=57'>1Ch 6:57</a> <br/> - Sennacherib besieged; his army defeated near<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=19&verse=8'>2Ki 19:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=19&verse=35'>2Ki 19:35</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=37&verse=36'>Isa 37:36</a> "}]}